task.summary: Default task
github installation
Created draft version of entities model. Created draft classes Client, Contract, Option, Tariff.
Added scheme of application web pages.

In project added JPA. Class Client converted in entity and linked with ecare.client table using DAO classes AbstractClientDAO and SqlClientDao with JPA methods. All CRUD and getAll() methods now working.
All entity classes linked with their DB tables. Workability now checked only at class Client.
Fixed entities Client and Contract (workability of creation of client with contracts list checked). Added abstract and SQL DAO for entity Contract.
Created all SQL DAO for all entities. Started writing of jUnit test for DAO's workability checking.
In all DAO's added methods deleteAll() and size(). In ClientAndContractDAOTest creation, loading and updating now working for client and tests pass. testDelete() not working yet.
Fixed all DAO's. Finished tests for all Entities DAO. All tests are working except testDeleteContract() and testDeleteOption(). Created ECareException class.
Created business logic for all DAO's. Transaction control moved to business classes from DAO. Fixed ECareException.

Created connected_option and incompatible_option tables in ecare scheme and dependence with class Option for them. Added option control methods with logic in OptionBusiness class and block/unblock methods with logic in ClientBusiness class.
Fixed option control logic. Added TestServlet class and JSP pages client, dashoboard, login and error for checking of authorization work. Authorization worked.

In ContractBusiness/ContractDAO added method findContractByNumber(). Added Dashboard, ContractCreation, Registration, Client and Contract servlets with jsp pages. Minimum functionality of client registration and creation of contract for client now working.
Added Tariff and Option Servlets and JSP for operator's functionality
Added servlets and JSP pages for changing of tariff for client (chooseTariff, chooseOptions). Fixed other servlets and pages.
Created interfaces for all services/business
Refactor DAO classes and services
All native SQL queries converted to named queries in entities
All DAO's and services converted in singletons
Added logger (singleton) in project, logging and more handling of exception in services.
Created jUnit tests for all services
